        {
            "id": 6070454,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 3M(MMM-US)大跌5.02%，報151.06美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>3M(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MMM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MMM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MMM-US</a>)截至台北時間19日00:56股價下跌7.98美元，報151.06美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量5,881,117（股），盤中最高價164.15美元、最低價151.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.17%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.17%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>3M(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MMM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MMM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MMM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.09%</li> <li>近 1 月：+11.83%</li> <li>近 3 月：+22.14%</li> <li>近 6 月：+14.27%</li> <li>今年以來：+23.2%</li></ul></section></main>",
